= V2 Verdict Debate Pattern =

{{info}}
Target verdict adjudication pattern. V2 preserves structured adversarial adjudication while routing prompt/model mechanics through the shared gateway.
{{/info}}

{{mermaid}}
flowchart LR
    E["ClaimContract<br/>EvidenceCorpus<br/>BoundarySet"] --> ADV["Advocate<br/>evidence-backed baseline"]

    ADV --> SC["Self-consistency / stability<br/>policy-owned repetitions"]
    ADV --> CH["Challenger<br/>counter-evidence only"]
    SC --> REC["Reconciliation<br/>evidence-weighted synthesis"]
    CH --> REC
    REC --> VAL["Validation<br/>citations, grounding, direction"]
    VAL --> G4{{"Gate 4<br/>confidence integrity"}}
    G4 --> VS["VerdictSet"]

    LLM["Prompt / Model / LLM Gateway"] -.-> ADV
    LLM -.-> SC
    LLM -.-> CH
    LLM -.-> REC
    LLM -.-> VAL
    WARN["Warning/Event Policy"] -.-> G4
    WARN -.-> VS

    classDef role fill:#e8f4ff,stroke:#2463a7,color:#08233d
    classDef gate fill:#fff4d6,stroke:#9a6700,color:#3a2600
    classDef output fill:#edf7ed,stroke:#3d8b40,color:#102a12
    classDef gateway fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2,color:#2a103f
    class ADV,SC,CH,REC,VAL role
    class G4 gate
    class E,VS output
    class LLM,WARN gateway
{{/mermaid}}
